---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SubscribeForm from '../components/SubscribeForm.astro';
---

<Layout title="Milestone Archive - ByteLite" description="Archive of ByteLite, Deep Kore / AIya, and HeartStrings milestones. For current status, visit /status.">
  <section class="news-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="status-redirect-notice">
        For current live/preview/development state, see the <a href="/status">Status Board</a>. This page is a historical milestone archive.
      </div>
      <h1 class="page-title">Milestone Archive</h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">A record of development milestones across ByteLite, Deep Kore, and HeartStrings</p>

      <!-- Key Updates -->
      <div class="updates-section">
        <h3>Development Milestones</h3>

        <div class="update-item highlight">
          <div class="update-date">Jan 2026</div>
          <div class="update-content">
            <h4>2026 Status Update - Site Audit and Verification Artifacts in Preparation</h4>
            <p>
              Website copy and disclosure audit completed. Terminology standardized across site.
              BME specification implemented and undergoing verification testing.
              Demonstration harness in development.
              All compression claims reflect controlled tests on enwik9 corpus; results depend on data structure and may vary.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="update-item">
          <div class="update-date">Nov 2025</div>
          <div class="update-content">
            <h4>BME Specification Implemented - Verification Underway</h4>
            <p>
              ByteLite's BME specification has been implemented and is in verification phase.
              Controlled test results on structured text corpora are under ongoing review.
              The headline "1GB to 15 bytes" figure has since been retracted pending full S-formula independent verification.
              Verification harness in development.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="update-item">
          <div class="update-date">Oct 2025</div>
          <div class="update-content">
            <h4>Deep Kore Architecture Research Reaches 50% Milestone</h4>
            <p>
              Deep Kore architecture research continues methodically under Genesis Goal Keeper governance framework.
              Mathematical proofs showing promise, with implementation proceeding safely and transparently
              at 50% completion.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="update-item">
          <div class="update-date">Sept 2025</div>
          <div class="update-content">
            <h4>Genesis Goal Keeper Now Fully Operational</h4>
            <p>
              Governance framework Genesis Goal Keeper is now fully operational, providing
              comprehensive safety protocols and oversight for all Deep Kore research.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="update-item">
          <div class="update-date">Aug 2025</div>
          <div class="update-content">
            <h4>HeartStrings Play Design Finalized</h4>
            <p>
              HeartStrings Play board game design milestone: six-tier card progression, component spec,
              and full ruleset. Physical prototype in preparation.
              ByteLite compression work continues in parallel.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="update-item">
          <div class="update-date">June 2025</div>
          <div class="update-content">
            <h4>Deep Kore Research & Access Status</h4>
            <p>
              ByteLite's compression mathematics revealed potential architectural applications beyond storage.
              Deep Kore research proceeds under Genesis Goal Keeper governance.
              Enterprise clients work directly with our team.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="update-item">
          <div class="update-date">May 2025</div>
          <div class="update-content">
            <h4>Patent Protection Secured</h4>
            <p>
              USPTO Provisional Patent 63/807,027 filed for "DATA COMPRESSION AND DECOMPRESSION PIPELINE,"
              protecting ByteLite's Bit Motion Encoding compression architecture.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="update-item">
          <div class="update-date">Q4 2024</div>
          <div class="update-content">
            <h4>The Discovery</h4>
            <p>
              While developing HeartStrings, founder Tash Broadwater identifies the compression architecture that becomes ByteLite.
              Initial controlled tests on the enwik9 corpus show extreme convergence. Results were later flagged for independent
              verification before public headline use.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Subscribe Section -->
      <div class="subscribe-wrapper">
        <div class="subscribe-intro">
          <h3>Get Milestone Updates</h3>
          <p>
            Updates go out when milestones are reached across HeartStrings Play, HeartStrings App,
            ByteLite, and Deep Kore / AIya.
          </p>
        </div>
        <SubscribeForm variant="compact" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .status-redirect-notice {
    background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.07);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.25);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 0.875rem 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.8);
  }

  .status-redirect-notice a {
    color: #00D4FF;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .status-redirect-notice a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  /* News Content */
  .news-content {
    padding: 3rem 0 3rem;
    background: var(--color-bg-darker);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  /* Page Title */
  .page-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-secondary) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 0 3rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Updates Section */
  .updates-section {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .updates-section h3 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .update-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr;
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.6);
    border: 1px solid rgba(224, 224, 224, 0.1);
    border-radius: 12px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .update-item:hover {
    transform: translateX(5px);
    border-color: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
    box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .update-item.highlight {
    border-color: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.4);
    background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.05);
  }

  .update-date {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    padding-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .update-content h4 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .update-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* Subscribe Section */
  .subscribe-wrapper {
    background: rgba(10, 14, 39, 0.6);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 3rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .subscribe-intro {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .subscribe-intro h3 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .subscribe-intro p {
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-title {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .page-subtitle {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .latest-announcement {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .announcement-header {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .latest-announcement h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .update-item {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .update-date {
      color: var(--color-secondary);
    }

    .subscribe-wrapper {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>